WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.000
Rock formations create geometric wonders!

00:00:03.000 --> 00:00:08.000
Mountains are built from layers we can measure and count.

00:00:08.000 --> 00:00:12.000
Angles, shapes, and patterns appear in natural rock structures.

00:00:12.000 --> 00:00:16.000
Geology and mathematics work together to tell Earth's story.

00:00:16.000 --> 00:00:20.000
Let's explore the maths hidden in mountain landscapes!